*Локация*: Ларнака, от офиса до моря 10 минут пешком.

*Leading/ Senior Data Analyst*

You will be responsible for sales and revenue reporting of the whole airline.

*Key responsibilities:*
- Manage  reporting based on data warehouse;
- Create SQL reports to further provide visibility to Sales, Operations, and Accounting;
- Collaborate with management to prioritize business and information needs;
- Apply fixes and rectify data structure issue or data processing flows.

*Requirements:*
- Experienced Leading/ Senior Data Analyst.
- Bachelor’s degree (master’s preferred) in Information Technology, Economics, Statistics, Applied Math, Business Administration, or any other related field;
- Extensive knowledge of SQL;
- Experience with BI &amp; visualization tools such as Tableau;
- Experience with PostgreSQL and/or Oracle database querying;
- English – upper intermediate or higher;
- Python experience as a plus;
- Experience in BI consulting as plus;
- Experience in corporate reporting systems implementation is a plus.

*Corporate benefits:*
- Medical scheme is covered 50% by the company;
- Staff travel with big discount (employee pays taxes and a millage amount).

*Relocation support:*
- Visa process support (incl. visa expenses compensation);
- Visa expense compensation.

